{"tid":1550941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫前線澄清一樣野，咁多鏡頭你叫佢郁手打藍絲？","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T22:00:56.000Z","uid":119729,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5891cb08c3106c9827e77f6036e55f848b174a","tid":1550941,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:54:54.000Z","msg":"現實係有好多私了，親眼見過三單；<br />\n記者唔係現場，快手私了速逃。<br />\n<br />\n當記者係晒現場時，郁手既畫面真係會好肉酸。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好再屌手足好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地係live見唔到，唔代表係無發生。"},{"pid":"83828b7bed4fb4e0c1cb545bd3a442f24a4dec4f","tid":1550941,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d5e906c4c8b925eb66d5d60f30f574898a2d8f7","tid":1550941,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-